# Conversion Priorities and Feature Mapping

## Critical Features (Must Have)

### 1. Profile Mode Home Page
**Priority**: Highest
**Hugo Reference**: [hugo-PaperMod/layouts/partials/index_profile.html](mdc:hugo-PaperMod/layouts/partials/index_profile.html)
**Implementation**: 
- Centered layout with avatar/image
- Title and subtitle display
- Social icons integration
- Custom buttons with external link indicators
- Responsive design

### 2. Light/Dark Mode Toggle
**Priority**: Highest
**Hugo Reference**: Theme toggle functionality in PaperMod
**Implementation**:
- System preference detection
- Manual toggle with persistence
- Smooth transitions between themes
- Icon-based toggle button

### 3. Blog Posts System
**Priority**: High
**Hugo Reference**: 
- [hugo-PaperMod/layouts/_default/list.html](mdc:hugo-PaperMod/layouts/_default/list.html)
- [hugo-PaperMod/layouts/_default/single.html](mdc:hugo-PaperMod/layouts/_default/single.html)
**Implementation**:
- Blog post listing page
- Individual post pages
- Post metadata (date, tags, reading time)
- Post navigation (next/previous)

### 4. Search Functionality
**Priority**: High
**Hugo Reference**: [hugo-PaperMod/layouts/_default/search.html](mdc:hugo-PaperMod/layouts/_default/search.html)
**Implementation**:
- Client-side search with keyboard shortcuts
- Search dialog/modal
- Real-time search results
- Search index generation

## Important Features (Should Have)

### 5. About Page
**Priority**: Medium
**Implementation**:
- Clean content layout
- Markdown content support
- Consistent with site theme

### 6. Navigation System
**Priority**: Medium
**Hugo Reference**: [hugo-PaperMod/layouts/partials/header.html](mdc:hugo-PaperMod/layouts/partials/header.html)
**Implementation**:
- Header navigation
- Mobile-responsive menu
- Active page indicators

### 7. Social Icons
**Priority**: Medium
**Hugo Reference**: [hugo-PaperMod/layouts/partials/social_icons.html](mdc:hugo-PaperMod/layouts/partials/social_icons.html)
**Implementation**:
- Comprehensive icon set
- Configurable social links
- Consistent styling

